summary: The initial Linkstash bookmark manager on Bun, SvelteKit, and Drizzle/LibSQL, backed by API integration tests.
---
The first cut of Linkstash: a fast, self-hostable bookmark manager built on **Bun + SvelteKit + Drizzle/LibSQL**, with API integration tests. The package was renamed from `proomptal-linkstash` to `aylith-linkstash`.
